name: 2025 9th International Conference on Computer, Software and Modeling
content: Publication: Accepted papers will be published into ICCSM 2025 Conference Proceedings, and submitted for indexing by Ei Compendex and Scopus, etc. Some accepted papers will be published in Journal of Software with at least 40% new content and indexed by DBLP, EBSCO, DOAJ, ProQuest, INSPEC, WorldCat, CNKI, etc.
